c: 2
v: 260
t: "When Abraham said: \"Show me, Lord, how You will raise the dead, \" He replied: \"Have you no faith?\" He said \"Yes, but just to reassure my heart.\" Allah said, \"Take four birds, draw them to you, and cut their bodies to pieces. Scatter them over the mountain-tops, then call them back. They will come swiftly to you. Know that Allah is Mighty, Wise"